data.description: Seller is offering $5k to buyers closing costs or rate buy down. This townhome is ready for it's next owner. It is  a two bedroom with a half bath down stairs and a full bath upstairs. The roof was replaced in 2020. And the bathrooms have brand new toilet and a new storm door was put in this year.  There is a current transferrable termite bond on the home and a home warranty that will transfer to the new owner. This home is in the middle of it all! Schedule your showing today.
